1. *Pitanju* je potrebno mnogo vremena da se reši. (It takes a lot of time to solve this question.)
2. Otac je obratio pažnju na *pitanju* svoje dece. (The father paid attention to his children's question.)
3. Ovo *pitanju* ostaje otvoreno. (This question remains open.)
4. Ona je dala odgovore na sva *pitanja*. (She answered all the questions.)
5. Rečeno je da će se *pitanju* obratiti pažnja. (It was said that attention will be paid to this question.)